Get GitHub rate limit

Source: R/get_gh_ratelimit.R
get_gh_ratelimit.Rd

Get GitHub rate limit

get_gh_ratelimit(github_token = Sys.getenv("GITHUB_PAT"))

Arguments

github_token

token passed to gh (default: Sys.getenv("GITHUB_PAT")

Value

overview of rate limit

Examples

get_gh_ratelimit()

#> # A tibble: 6 x 5
#>   id                   limit  used remaining      reset
#>   <chr>                <int> <int>     <int>      <int>
#> 1 core                  5000   932      4068 1622643997
#> 2 search                  30     0        30 1622643870
#> 3 graphql               5000    31      4969 1622644497
#> 4 integration_manifest  5000     0      5000 1622647410
#> 5 source_import          100     0       100 1622643870
#> 6 code_scanning_upload   500     0       500 1622647410
